lead_paragraph: Alex Naddour stops himself in mid-thought, his brain tapping the brakes so he can stress that he's aware his spot on the 2016 U.S. men's Olympic gymnastics team is not simply the result of the force of his considerable will.

headline.print_headline: Alternate No More, Naddour Counts Blessings on Road to Rio
